{
  "stem": "26142.15",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The Russians, by that time, this was in May.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I might be wrong here with the dates.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] The-- the Polish uprising started about that time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we-- we were at the outside of the city.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The city was burning.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the Russians were first, crossed the Vistula river around, around the city of Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But we didn't know it then.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We know it now what happened that Stalin ordered-- because the uprising of the city Warsaw was under the tutelage of the Polish government in exile in London, and they didn't want that government to be successful.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because it was the London government, it would be more allied with the West.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So they-- they pulled their forces back from across the Vistula River.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The Vistula divides the city of-- of Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they let the city burn to a crisp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And-- and-- and they wouldn't give them any help.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We were on this side.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we were watching the city-- the city burn-- burn down.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] It's-- it's-- and I found out months later that the-- the Warsaw ghetto was burned-- was burned down in 1943.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But we didn't know about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We were so close.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We didn't know about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I remember sitting close by the city in Wlochy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And there was an old Pole sitting on-- on a bench and watching, seeing that the city is on fire.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And-- and at night time, it-- it was awful, awful sight to see a city going up in fire.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "The Germans had a special group, Ukrainians, trained.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And they went-- surrounded the city.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And they went from block to block, whatever they could take out from the housing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And they were just-- just burning the city down.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
